{
  "stem": "22883.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Do you want me to elaborate that and use more details about that?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "First tell us her name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "What was her at the time?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, at that time, her name was not real, but the assumed name, a false name, because she had already the documented identification, false document identification.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And her name at that time was Sofia Palchek.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Real name was Lily Goldsobel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But at that time was hidden.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I-- when I met her, and this meeting was just to get acquainted who-- who the person is-- this is through the friends.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I had friends who knew my-- my wife even before the war, because they were going for vacations together-- well, together, to the same place.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was [NON-ENGLISH], not far from Warsaw, 30 kilometers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the Goldsobel family was coming there for vacation, and-- and the family of-- of-- of her-- of this friend of mine was also coming there.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a girl.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she heard-- there was a girl and-- and-- and boy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] who knew the family of Goldsobel.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And apparently, this boy, he knew Lilian before the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and that's the-- the-- guy who-- [SIGHS] delivered this first document for Lilian to come out-- out of ghetto.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And-- and that's what-- and at that time, it was 1943, spring 1943.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He asked his sister to approach me and to find out if I could arrange something that she could go to Germany to-- to find some-- some job, let's say, in hotel or something, which will give her the chance to survive the war.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So she did that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I came.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was my first [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] meeting her.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
